This paper discusses the issue of cellular wireless roaming charges and the competition among Internet Service Providers (ISPs) in the market. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also touches upon issues related to information theory (cs.IT), security and privacy (cs.CR), computational complexity (cs.CC), and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, these categories are less likely as they are not the main focus of the paper.
